T1  - When Liability Is Not Enough: Regulating Bonus Payments in Markets with Advice
AU  - Honda, Jun
AU  - Inderst, Roman
AU  - Ottaviani, Marco
Y1  - 2023/04/11
PY  - 2023
DA  - 2024/02/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2023.4750
